Sergey (1 Aug 2023)

- urlapi: fix heap buffer overflow

  `u->path = Curl_memdup(path, pathlen + 1);` accesses bytes after the null-ter
  minator.

  ```
  ==2676==ERROR: AddressSanitizer: heap-buffer-overflow on address 0x04d48c75 a
